    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The return type of the function is likely a boolean or integer, indicating whether the transaction type is valid. The structure is a single scalar value, which is typical for scalar functions. This value is used in queries to filter or validate data based on transaction type."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
